## Additional Attribution

This project uses the ASHRAE Global Thermal Comfort Database II and India
thermal comfort dataset for model training and validation.

Dataset sources:
- ASHRAE Global Thermal Comfort Database II: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/claytonmiller/ashrae-global-thermal-comfort-database-ii
- India Thermal Comfort Dataset: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/claytonmiller/ashrae-global-thermal-comfort-database-ii

The thermal comfort prediction models are trained using machine learning
techniques including Random Forest algorithms.
